Mark where you plan to cut with your Sharpie marker and then cut along the lines with a saw. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b3/Make-a-Birch-Tree-Curtain-Rod-Step-1Bullet2-Version-2.jpg/v4-459px-Make-a-Birch-Tree-Curtain-Rod-Step-1Bullet2-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b3/Make-a-Birch-Tree-Curtain-Rod-Step-1Bullet2-Version-2.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Birch-Tree-Curtain-Rod-Step-1Bullet2-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fair_use">Fair Use</a> (screenshot)<br>
</p></div>"} Cover branches with polyurethane. In a well-ventilated area, use a paintbrush to cover the branches with polyurethane. This will keep the branches sealed and protected from peeling or flaking. Allow branches to dry overnight in a cool, dry room. Mount branch “v” brackets against the window molding. For best results, measure the molding to determine exactly where the brackets will be placed and to ensure they are level and equal. Drill screws directly through branch brackets and into the molding. Use 2 screws per branch bracket, one toward the “v” and the other toward the bottom of the branch. Lay branch rod into the branch brackets. You may want to test how it will look before you add curtain panels or just slip the panel loops through the branch rod and hang. Hang your curtain. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f8/Make-a-Birch-Tree-Curtain-Rod-Step-4Bullet1-Version-2.jpg/v4-459px-Make-a-Birch-Tree-Curtain-Rod-Step-4Bullet1-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f8/Make-a-Birch-Tree-Curtain-Rod-Step-4Bullet1-Version-2.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Birch-Tree-Curtain-Rod-Step-4Bullet1-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fair_use">Fair Use</a> (screenshot)<br>
